<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Doune & Grem — 28 mai 2028</title>
<meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400&family=EB+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;1,400&family=Jost:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --ivory:#F6F1E6;
    --navy:#1B2A40;
    --lavender:#8C87A6;
    --olive:#6E7857;
    --gold:#B08D57;
    --charcoal:#2B2924;
    --line:rgba(27,42,64,0.14);
    --radius:2px;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box;}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
  body{
    margin:0;
    background:var(--ivory);
    color:var(--charcoal);
    font-family:'EB Garamond', serif;
    font-size:18px;
    line-height:1.65;
    -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
  }
  h1,h2,h3{
    font-family:'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-weight:500;
    margin:0 0 0.4em;
    color:var(--navy);
  }
  .eyebrow{
    font-family:'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size:0.72rem;
    letter-spacing:0.28em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--olive);
    display:block;
    margin-bottom:0.9em;
  }
  a{color:inherit;}
  .wrap{max-width:760px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 28px;}

  /* ---------- ACCESS GATE ---------- */
  #gate{
    position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:50;
    background:var(--navy);
    color:var(--ivory);
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    padding:24px;
    transition:opacity 0.9s ease, visibility 0.9s ease;
  }
  #gate.hidden{opacity:0;visibility:hidden;pointer-events:none;}
  .gate-card{max-width:420px;width:100%;text-align:center;}
  .tulip{width:64px;height:auto;margin:0 auto 28px;display:block;opacity:0.92;}
  .gate-card h1{
    color:var(--ivory);
    font-size:2.1rem;
    font-style:italic;
    letter-spacing:0.02em;
  }
  .gate-card .eyebrow{color:var(--lavender);}
  .gate-sub{
    font-size:0.95rem;
    color:rgba(246,241,230,0.72);
    margin-bottom:2em;
  }
  .code-form{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;align-items:center;}
  #code-input{
    width:100%;
    max-width:280px;
    background:transparent;
    border:none;
    border-bottom:1px solid rgba(246,241,230,0.4);
    color:var(--ivory);
    font-family:'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size:1rem;
    letter-spacing:0.35em;
    text-align:center;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    padding:10px 0;
    outline:none;
  }
  #code-input::placeholder{color:rgba(246,241,230,0.35);letter-spacing:0.2em;}
  #code-input:focus{border-bottom-color:var(--gold);}
  .gate-btn{
    font-family:'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size:0.78rem;
    letter-spacing:0.2em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    background:none;
    border:1px solid var(--gold);
    color:var(--gold);
    padding:12px 30px;
    cursor:pointer;
    border-radius:var(--radius);
    transition:background 0.25s ease, color 0.25s ease;
  }
  .gate-btn:hover{background:var(--gold);color:var(--navy);}
  .gate-error{
    font-family:'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size:0.78rem;
    color:#D98C6B;
    height:1.2em;
    letter-spacing:0.05em;
  }

  /* ---------- SITE ---------- */
  #site{display:none;}
  #site.visible{display:block;}

  header.hero{
    padding:110px 0 90px;
    text-align:center;
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  header.hero .tulip{width:46px;margin-bottom:22px;opacity:0.8;}
  header.hero h1{
    font-size:3.2rem;
    font-style:italic;
  }
  header.hero .amp{color:var(--gold);font-style:normal;padding:0 10px;}
  header.hero .date{
    font-family:'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size:0.85rem;
    letter-spacing:0.25em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--olive);
    margin-top:18px;
  }

  section{padding:86px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);}
  section.dark{
    background:var(--navy);
    color:var(--ivory);
    border-bottom:none;
  }
  section.dark h2{color:var(--ivory);}
  section.dark .eyebrow{color:var(--lavender);}
  section.dark .line{background:rgba(246,241,230,0.18);}

  .center{text-align:center;}
  .line{width:40px;height:1px;background:var(--line);margin:26px auto 0;}

  /* countdown */
  #countdown{
    display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:34px;flex-wrap:wrap;
    margin-top:18px;
  }
  #countdown .unit{text-align:center;}
  #countdown .num{
    font-family:'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size:3rem;
    color:var(--navy);
    line-height:1;
  }
  #countdown .lab{
    font-family:'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size:0.68rem;
    letter-spacing:0.2em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--olive);
    display:block;
    margin-top:6px;
  }

  /* programme */
  .timeline{margin-top:40px;}
  .tl-item{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:110px 1fr;
    gap:24px;
    padding:20px 0;
    border-top:1px solid rgba(246,241,230,0.14);
  }
  .tl-item:first-child{border-top:none;}
  .tl-time{
    font-family:'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size:0.85rem;
    letter-spacing:0.05em;
    color:var(--gold);
    padding-top:2px;
  }
  .tl-item h3{color:var(--ivory);font-size:1.3rem;margin-bottom:4px;}
  .tl-item p{margin:0;color:rgba(246,241,230,0.78);font-size:0.98rem;}

  /* venue / info grid */
  .info-grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
    gap:36px;
    margin-top:36px;
  }
  .info-block h3{font-size:1.15rem;margin-bottom:8px;}
  .info-block p{margin:0;color:var(--charcoal);}
  .info-block .eyebrow{margin-bottom:0.5em;}

  /* dress code */
  .swatches{display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;margin:30px 0 10px;}
  .swatch{width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:50%;border:1px solid var(--line);}

  /* RSVP */
  form.rsvp{max-width:480px;margin:40px auto 0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:20px;}
  .field{text-align:left;}
  .field label{
    display:block;
    font-family:'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size:0.7rem;
    letter-spacing:0.15em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--olive);
    margin-bottom:6px;
  }
  .field input,.field select,.field textarea{
    width:100%;
    font-family:'EB Garamond', serif;
    font-size:1rem;
    padding:10px 2px;
    border:none;
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
    background:transparent;
    color:var(--charcoal);
    outline:none;
  }
  .field input:focus,.field select:focus,.field textarea:focus{border-bottom-color:var(--gold);}
  .submit-btn{
    align-self:center;
    margin-top:10px;
    font-family:'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size:0.78rem;
    letter-spacing:0.2em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    background:var(--navy);
    color:var(--ivory);
    border:none;
    padding:14px 34px;
    cursor:pointer;
    border-radius:var(--radius);
    transition:background 0.25s ease;
  }
  .submit-btn:hover{background:var(--olive);}
  .rsvp-note{
    font-size:0.85rem;
    color:var(--olive);
    text-align:center;
    margin-top:14px;
  }

  /* cagnotte */
  .cagnotte-box{
    max-width:420px;margin:34px auto 0;
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    padding:30px;
    text-align:center;
  }
  .cagnotte-box a{
    display:inline-block;margin-top:16px;
    font-family:'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size:0.78rem;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--gold);border-bottom:1px solid var(--gold);padding-bottom:2px;
  }

  /* FAQ */
  .faq-item{padding:22px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--line);}
  .faq-item:first-child{border-top:none;}
  .faq-item h3{font-size:1.1rem;}
  .faq-item p{margin:6px 0 0;}

  footer{
    padding:56px 0;text-align:center;
    font-family:'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size:0.72rem;
    letter-spacing:0.15em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--olive);
  }

  @media(max-width:640px){
    header.hero h1{font-size:2.3rem;}
    .info-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    #countdown{gap:20px;}
    #countdown .num{font-size:2.2rem;}
    .tl-item{grid-template-columns:80px 1fr;}
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){
    html{scroll-behavior:auto;}
    #gate{transition:none;}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- ============ ACCESS GATE ============ -->
  <div id="gate">
    <div class="gate-card">
      <svg class="tulip" viewBox="0 0 60 90" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M30 40 C15 40 12 20 18 8 C22 15 26 18 30 18 C34 18 38 15 42 8 C48 20 45 40 30 40Z" stroke="#F6F1E6" stroke-width="1.1"/>
        <path d="M30 18 V 4" stroke="#F6F1E6" stroke-width="1.1"/>
        <path d="M30 40 L30 78" stroke="#F6F1E6" stroke-width="1.1"/>
        <path d="M30 55 C22 55 18 62 16 70" stroke="#F6F1E6" stroke-width="1.1"/>
        <path d="M30 62 C38 62 42 68 44 74" stroke="#F6F1E6" stroke-width="1.1"/>
      </svg>
      <span class="eyebrow">Accès invités</span>
      <h1>Doune &amp; Grem</h1>
      <p class="gate-sub">Entrez le code d'invitation pour découvrir tous les détails du mariage.</p>
      <div class="code-form">
        <input id="code-input" type="text" placeholder="Code d'invitation" autocomplete="off">
        <button class="gate-btn" onclick="checkCode()">Entrer</button>
        <div class="gate-error" id="gate-error"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ============ SITE ============ -->
  <div id="site">

    <header class="hero">
      <div class="wrap">
        <svg class="tulip" viewBox="0 0 60 90" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M30 40 C15 40 12 20 18 8 C22 15 26 18 30 18 C34 18 38 15 42 8 C48 20 45 40 30 40Z" stroke="#1B2A40" stroke-width="1.1"/>
          <path d="M30 18 V 4" stroke="#1B2A40" stroke-width="1.1"/>
          <path d="M30 40 L30 78" stroke="#1B2A40" stroke-width="1.1"/>
          <path d="M30 55 C22 55 18 62 16 70" stroke="#1B2A40" stroke-width="1.1"/>
          <path d="M30 62 C38 62 42 68 44 74" stroke="#1B2A40" stroke-width="1.1"/>
        </svg>
        <h1>Doune <span class="amp">&amp;</span> Grem</h1>
        <div class="date">Samedi 28 Mai 2028 — Provence, France</div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- COUNTDOWN -->
    <section class="center">
      <div class="wrap">
        <span class="eyebrow">Compte à rebours</span>
        <h2>Il reste encore un peu de patience</h2>
        <div id="countdown">
          <div class="unit"><span class="num" id="cd-days">--</span><span class="lab">Jours</span></div>
          <div class="unit"><span class="num" id="cd-hours">--</span><span class="lab">Heures</span></div>
          <div class="unit"><span class="num" id="cd-min">--</span><span class="lab">Minutes</span></div>
          <div class="unit"><span class="num" id="cd-sec">--</span><span class="lab">Secondes</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- NOTRE HISTOIRE -->
    <section>
      <div class="wrap center">
        <span class="eyebrow">Notre histoire</span>
        <h2>Comment tout a commencé</h2>
        <div class="line"></div>
        <p style="max-width:560px;margin:26px auto 0;text-align:left;">
          [À compléter — racontez ici votre rencontre, un souvenir marquant, et le moment de la demande.
          Ce texte est un espace réservé : remplacez-le par votre histoire, telle que vous voulez la partager
          avec vos invités.]
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PROGRAMME -->
    <section class="dark">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="center">
          <span class="eyebrow">Le jour J</span>
          <h2 style="color:var(--ivory);">Programme du weekend</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline">
          <div class="tl-item">
            <div class="tl-time">Ven. 26 mai</div>
            <div><h3>Arrivée &amp; dîner d'accueil</h3><p>Installation au gîte, apéritif et dîner convivial pour ouvrir le weekend.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="tl-item">
            <div class="tl-time">Sam. 28 mai — 15h</div>
            <div><h3>Cérémonie</h3><p>[Lieu de la cérémonie], suivie du vin d'honneur dans les jardins.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="tl-item">
            <div class="tl-time">Sam. 28 mai — 20h</div>
            <div><h3>Dîner &amp; soirée</h3><p>Dîner assis puis ouverture de la piste de danse jusqu'au bout de la nuit.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="tl-item">
            <div class="tl-time">Dim. 29 mai</div>
            <div><h3>Brunch de clôture</h3><p>Un dernier moment ensemble avant les départs, dans la matinée.</p></div>
